title: BONE-Net: A novel hybrid deep-learning model for effective osteoporosis detection
venue: PLOS ONE, accepted with minor revision
excerpt: This paper presents BONE-Net, a hybrid deep-learning model combining DenseNet169, Vision Transformer, and an Attention Module for osteoporosis detection.
